---
import { siteConfig } from '../data/site';
---

<section id="tentang" class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16 animate-on-scroll">
      <span class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-stone-400">Tentang Kami</span>
      <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-3xl sm:text-4xl tracking-tight text-stone-900 mt-3 mb-4">
        Cerita di Balik Miro Mie
      </h2>
      <p class="text-stone-500 max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Dimulai dari {siteConfig.year}, kami hadir untuk menyajikan cita rasa mie & baso terbaik.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Photo -->
      <div class="animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="aspect-[4/3] rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555396273-367ea4eb4db5?w=800&q=80&auto=format"
            alt="Suasana Miro Mie"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="animate-on-scroll">
        <blockquote class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-heading font-medium text-stone-800 mb-6 leading-relaxed border-l-2 border-red-700 pl-6">
          "Kami percaya, makanan yang enak dimulai dari bahan yang segar dan racikan yang tulus."
        </blockquote>

        <p class="text-stone-500 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Miro Mie lahir dari kecintaan terhadap kuliner nusantara. Dengan resep turun-temurun dan bahan pilihan,
          kami menyajikan Mie Yamin, Baso, Mie Ayam, dan Es Teler yang tak hanya lezat, tapi juga menghadirkan
          kenangan rasa yang bikin kembali lagi.
        </p>

        <!-- 4 Feature Cards -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3.5 rounded-lg bg-stone-50 border border-stone-100">
            <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-white rounded-lg border border-stone-200 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-emerald-600"><path d="M11 20A7 7 0 0 1 9.8 6.9C15.5 4.9 17 3.5 17 3.5s1.5 2 1.5 5.5A7 7 0 0 1 11 20z"/><path d="M11 20v-8"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-900 text-sm">Bahan Segar</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-stone-500 mt-0.5">Dipilih setiap pagi</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3.5 rounded-lg bg-stone-50 border border-stone-100">
            <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-white rounded-lg border border-stone-200 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-stone-700"><path d="M6 13.87A4 4 0 0 1 7.41 6a5.11 5.11 0 0 1 1.05-1.54 5 5 0 0 1 7.08 0A5.11 5.11 0 0 1 16.59 6 4 4 0 0 1 18 13.87V21H6Z"/><line x1="6" y1="17" x2="18" y2="17"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-900 text-sm">Resep Turun-Temurun</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-stone-500 mt-0.5">Bumbu warisan keluarga</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3.5 rounded-lg bg-stone-50 border border-stone-100">
            <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-white rounded-lg border border-stone-200 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-stone-700"><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-900 text-sm">Harga Terjangkau</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-stone-500 mt-0.5">Ramah di kantong</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3.5 rounded-lg bg-stone-50 border border-stone-100">
            <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-white rounded-lg border border-stone-200 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-stone-700"><path d="m3 9 9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-900 text-sm">Nyaman & Bersih</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-stone-500 mt-0.5">Cocok untuk keluarga</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>